==Hebrew==
===Proper noun===
'''אל''' (El) {{m}}

# [[God]]. (This form of the word is usually combined with another word, such as in [[גבריאל]] ([[Gabriel]]) or [[מיכאל]] ([[Michael]]), but it can also to refer to God, for example [[אל שדי]], "God [[Almighty]]" ([[שדי]]).)

===Noun===
'''אל''' (el) {{m}}

# [[god]], [[deity]]

===Adverb===
'''אל''' (al)

# [[not]], [[don't]]

===Preposition===
'''אל''' (el)

# [[to]], [[towards]], [[into]]
# [[at]], [[by]]

